title: Death of the Other (Con Panel Audio)
description:
(From Con of Thrones 2019 in Nashville) Fighting a war against immortal ice faeries and their zombie army is a tall order, but Wars and Politics of Ice and Fire and HoW are ready to discuss strategies, equipment, and techniques for defeating the Others and saving humanity. Panelists: Aziz and Something Like a Lawyer (Jim McGeehin) of Wars and Politics of Ice and Fire.
